{"tid":2435021,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"好多人想移民/走難去澳洲，原來呢邊就黎無廣東話","createTime":"2021-03-06T02:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T22:27:24.000Z","uid":378720,"like":61,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"2497fd04f3c599f2ec57ced36f13d13a310e8527","tid":2435021,"uid":378720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:36:34.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲冇睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，澳洲最受歡迎嘅廣東話頻道SBS廣東話係農曆新年開始盃合併做SBS中文，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">以後分分鐘俾隔離国語残体字食埋</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟而家係當地讀緊書，奈何唔知有咩可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。今朝瞓醒（對唔住我瞓到成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）見有當地港人組織發起一人一信直接搵總裁*投訴，想香港連登嘅大家都幫下手，唔係將來帶幾多人過到嚟都保唔住我地引以自豪嘅廣東話文化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1764116977186092/posts/2823186157945830/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1764116977186092%2Fposts%2F2823186157945830%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=e2e6aea7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1764116977186092/posts/2823186157945830/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n上邊係活動嘅link，望落好簡單，我啱啱都做咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望睇到嘅咁多位都幫幫手，知道香港近況好差晚晚瞓唔着，但海外戰線我地都要守住。如果廣東話係外國都失守我地連僅餘嘅士氣都會冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港人反抗！</span></span>"},{"pid":"42ae9af3b091aae5ae878445aceff09da15a3f77","tid":2435021,"uid":378720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:36:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"481cf896ef257dd394113481dfa2426f1ad8b080","tid":2435021,"uid":378720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:37:21.000Z","msg":"我柒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又P牌又不推文，有冇巴打幫幫手"},{"pid":"67b75e927e8ec4a22529768e1352877143733963","tid":2435021,"uid":226813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:38:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ae612ea143cf248b592af4fa6500131ecda15c5","tid":2435021,"uid":204929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:38:53.000Z","msg":"移民去澳洲?"},{"pid":"32bb32f6147e35f9b8dc773bed708e9abe28591f","tid":2435021,"uid":378720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:38:56.000Z","msg":"推唔郁都推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4e46b61541559497e0ec6d8cd5910f76bd17e0","tid":2435021,"uid":172959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"80cbcef1bc5c34311fedab472e72dd9e4c9c2496","tid":2435021,"uid":378720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:39:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f50575683ec6ac2043b6074dff4c00e54cb94e67","tid":2435021,"uid":59158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22f6c8488ec9beda6bf17d4f33d459e15ee7482","tid":2435021,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c671b2c7e69a0326dcc7ab58bf1ad507d3e3c0","tid":2435021,"uid":271711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:39:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0dc5484e63d127023f30ab638205e8a74368f24b","tid":2435021,"uid":378720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-